sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Admin
    participant CP as Control Panel
    participant API as Backend API
    participant REPO as Document Repository
    participant DB as Database
    participant OBJECT_STORAGE as MinIO Service
    participant VECTOR_DATABASE as OpenSearch Service

    Admin->>CP: 1. Pilih menu dokumen
    CP->>API: 2. GET Request /documents
    API->>REPO: 3. getAllDocuments()
    REPO->>DB: 4. Query data Document
    DB-->>REPO: 5. Data Document
    REPO-->>API: 5.1 Data Document
    API-->>CP: 5.2 Data Document
    CP->>Admin: 6. Menampilkan data dokumen
    Admin->>CP: 7. Klik menu "Aksi"
    CP->>Admin: 8. Menampilkan menu-menu aksi
    Admin->>CP: 9. Klik menu "Hapus"
    CP->>API: 10. DELETE Request /documents/{id}
    API->>API: 11. Validasi Input
    API->>OBJECT_STORAGE: 12. Delete file dari MinIO
    API->>VECTOR_DATABASE: 13. Delete embedding dokumen dari OpenSearch
    API->>REPO: 14. deleteDocument()
    REPO->>DB: 15. Delete data Document
    DB-->>REPO: 16. Pesan berhasil hapus dokumen
    REPO-->>API: 16.1 Pesan berhasil hapus dokumen
    API-->>CP: 16.2 Pesan berhasil hapus dokumen
    CP->>Admin: 17. Menampilkan pesan berhasil hapus dokumen
    CP->>Admin: 18. Redirect ke halaman dokumen